
Ranger Help for: underground
============================

SUMMARY:    
The underground terrain is characterized by enclosed natural walls and
is almost always dark and dank. Underground or cave Rangers feel at 
home in this inhospitable environment, gaining a feel for how a cave
runs just from listening. Ranger skills are somewhat limited in caves,
so the Ranger population is smaller here. The Underworld is the most
obvious example of the underground environment, although caves are
all over the realms.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

